{
  "stem": "20035.5",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then I found out-- the next day I found out that-- from my auntie who survived, who lived in another town, and found out that Mom was killed in Bergen-Belsen.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Bergen-Belsen, they were together.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And sometimes the end of March, Mom was killed.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mom died.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And basically, that settled my desire-- or forget about desire.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That settled my-- my time in Hungary.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I had no rhyme and reason to be there and I had no the-- no disposition whatsoever to do anything else but dislike the people who kicked me out, who took away-- I still say it today, they raped me of my-- of youth, of my-- my whole life, of love, of parents, of brother, of family.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What do I do there?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I have no rhyme or reason.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So a cousin who survived, the two of us, we decided that we are going to Germany.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And where did you go?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And we are going to go to DP camp if we have to.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And from there, we'll see what's going to happen to our life.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We went to a camp, Leipheim.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Leipheim is near Ulm, U-L-M.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Leipheim is L-E-I-P-H-E-I-M.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in Leipheim, basically we spent-- spent the time at the beginning with not too much, but not too much doing, not too much what I would call it constructive work.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Then suddenly children started to come in.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, I'm talking about I was a child, but I was already a big man.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was 17.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So you're 17, you're already a-- more than a child.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But little-- from one to five-year-old little orphans started to come in.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
